\begin_inset Formula $\alpha log(A_{t+1})+\beta log(\nu_{t+1})+(1-\alpha-\beta)log(\rho_{t+1})$
\end_inset

 is maximised.
 Since the consumer does not exercise any choice of 
\begin_inset Formula $\eta_{t}$
\end_inset

, we can focus on 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta log(c_{t+1})$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha log(A_{t+1})$
\end_inset

.
 A 
\begin_inset Formula $\nu_{t+1}$
\end_inset

 that maximises 
\begin_inset Formula $\upsilon(c_{t+1},A_{t+1},\rho)$
\end_inset

